&lt;/h1></description></item><item><title/><link>https://dpurge.github.io/docs/cloud/azure/exploring/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dpurge.github.io/docs/cloud/azure/exploring/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="exploring-azure-resources">
